description:
Jo Malone London's executive director of product development, Céline Roux, explains the magic that goes into making some of our favorite scents. Before that: L'Oréal's newest hair spokesperson steps down; a recap of Indie Beauty Expo L.A.; and why the masking trend shows no signs of slowing down.
